Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.37,0:00:34.26,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Conhecemos o Um Urso e a Himawari que foram amaldiçoados pelo Robe{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.26,0:00:37.18,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\i1}de modo a não poderem\N voltar a casa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:39.21,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\i1}É o espelho da verdade.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.21,0:00:42.77,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Diz a verdade da pessoa\N que estiver refletida no espelho.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.38,0:00:45.64,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pode ser-vos útil.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.27,0:00:49.27,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Temos de nos apressar a salvá-los.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.79,0:00:55.86,Normal,,0,0,0,,Olha para ali!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:58.75,Normal,,0,0,0,,Finalmente chegámos\N à Terra das Lágrimas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.75,0:01:01.41,Normal,,0,0,0,,Isto é a Terra das Lágrimas?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.41,0:01:03.79,Normal,,0,0,0,,Gyubid, aquele é o Castelo Maldito.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:05.58,Normal,,0,0,0,,Castelo Maldito?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.58,0:01:10.75,Normal,,0,0,0,,O {\i1}Sabbath{\i0} da Terra das Lágrimas\N faz-se todos os anos naquela torre.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:13.71,Normal,,0,0,0,,Então, a avó e o Kojima estão ali?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.11,0:01:16.68,Normal,,0,0,0,,Querem ir para ali?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.68,0:01:18.64,Normal,,0,0,0,,Um fantasma!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:20.14,Normal,,0,0,0,,Não sou um fantasma.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:21.60,Normal,,0,0,0,,Sou o Demónio da Neve.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:23.93,Normal,,0,0,0,,O {\i1}Sabbath{\i0} está a começar,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.93,0:01:25.97,Normal,,0,0,0,,por isso não me devo aproximar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.97,0:01:30.06,Normal,,0,0,0,,Posso levar-vos lá,\N mas vai custar-vos algo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.39,0:01:33.53,Normal,,0,0,0,,Os doces da Lollipop e da Cocoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.53,0:01:34.87,Normal,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:37.71,Normal,,0,0,0,,Aqueles que sabem bem\Nquando estão fresquinhos?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.71,0:01:40.51,Normal,,0,0,0,,Que bom, que bom!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.51,0:01:44.70,Normal,,0,0,0,,Não me importava de tos dar\Nem troca desse favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.35,0:01:47.14,Normal,,0,0,0,,Viva!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.13,0:01:50.94,Normal,,0,0,0,,É lindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.94,0:01:53.46,Normal,,0,0,0,,Não se larguem!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.85,0:01:59.88,Normal,,0,0,0,,Obrigada, Demónio da Neve.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:02.18,Normal,,0,0,0,,O {\i1}Sabbath{\i0} é realizado lá em cima.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.18,0:02:03.43,Normal,,0,0,0,,Tenham cuidado.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:05.08,Normal,,0,0,0,,Choco, anda.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.08,0:02:06.02,Normal,,0,0,0,,Boa sorte!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:06.77,Normal,,0,0,0,,Adeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:18.57,Normal,,0,0,0,,Avó! Kojima!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.06,0:02:19.97,Normal,,0,0,0,,Bandidas!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:20.86,Normal,,0,0,0,,Apanhem-nas!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:21.73,Normal,,0,0,0,,Esperem aí.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:25.41,Normal,,0,0,0,,Quem és tu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.72,0:02:29.74,Normal,,0,0,0,,Sou a neta da bruxa Tika,\N Kurotori Chiyoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.74,0:02:33.91,Normal,,0,0,0,,Devolve-me a minha avó \Ne o meu amigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.91,0:02:35.17,Normal,,0,0,0,,Nem pensar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:37.88,Normal,,0,0,0,,Robe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.33,0:02:40.85,Normal,,0,0,0,,Sua Majestade,\N Rainha da Terra das Lágrimas,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.85,0:02:45.16,Normal,,0,0,0,,vim para levar comigo a bruxa \Ndas trevas que está sob minha custódia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:49.89,Normal,,0,0,0,,Os pecados da bruxa Tika \Ntêm de ser levados ao tribunal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:53.27,Normal,,0,0,0,,Que prova me dás \Nda tua posição social?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:56.92,Normal,,0,0,0,,Treinei 13 bruxas, \Nobservei o seu sucesso
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:03:01.79,Normal,,0,0,0,,e o Rei da Terra do Sol \Nnomeou-me ser Inquisidor,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.79,0:03:04.95,Normal,,0,0,0,,deixando-me ao encargo \Nde todas as bruxas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:07.16,Normal,,0,0,0,,É esta a minha prova.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:11.22,Normal,,0,0,0,,Tu abandonaste\N a Himawari e o Um Urso!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.22,0:03:12.41,Normal,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.41,0:03:16.50,Normal,,0,0,0,,Se isso for verdade, \Nquebraste uma lei importante.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:19.48,Normal,,0,0,0,,Não é possível que o Rei da Terra do Sol
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:23.59,Normal,,0,0,0,,nomeasse alguém assim para seu Inquisidor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:27.35,Normal,,0,0,0,,Prendam estas pessoas por difamação.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:35.15,Normal,,0,0,0,,Choco, tens aí contigo \No espelho da verdade?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:37.00,Normal,,0,0,0,,O espelho da verdade?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.84,0:03:39.74,Normal,,0,0,0,,Estás a falar disto?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.12,0:03:42.49,Normal,,0,0,0,,Reflete o Robe nele.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:45.16,Normal,,0,0,0,,A verdade do Robe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.70,0:03:55.14,Normal,,0,0,0,,Sou o Robe Lu Puti, o Inquisidor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.14,0:03:57.67,Normal,,0,0,0,,É verdade que treinei dois humanos,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:04:00.17,Normal,,0,0,0,,mas como provaram não ser-me úteis,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:02.65,Normal,,0,0,0,,certifiquei-me \Nque não voltariam a usar magia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.65,0:04:05.26,Normal,,0,0,0,,Esse item é uma falsificação.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:10.18,Normal,,0,0,0,,Não, não é.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:14.52,Normal,,0,0,0,,Ninguém engana Gyubad, \Na Rainha da Terra das Lágrimas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:16.94,Normal,,0,0,0,,Gyubad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:19.46,Normal,,0,0,0,,Há quanto tempo, Gyubid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:21.74,Normal,,0,0,0,,Avó! Estás viva?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:27.59,Normal,,0,0,0,,Lamento, Choco.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:29.37,Normal,,0,0,0,,Não te queria enganar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:30.62,Normal,,0,0,0,,Avó!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:33.58,Normal,,0,0,0,,Eu pedi-lhe este favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:36.83,Normal,,0,0,0,,Não era esta a nossa estratégia?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:38.54,Normal,,0,0,0,,Prof. Melusine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:42.46,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Foram estas três que vi\N no álbum de fotografias,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:45.43,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as amigas da Escola Real de Magia!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:49.56,Normal,,0,0,0,,Quando soube que o Robe\N estava atrás da Tika,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:54.13,Normal,,0,0,0,,fizemos com que ele viesse para\N a Terra das Lágrimas, para o podermos julgar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:56.79,Normal,,0,0,0,,Mas era suposto\N ser a única prisioneira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:05:00.71,Normal,,0,0,0,,Nunca pensei que isto envolvesse\N o teu amigo, Choco.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:01.78,Normal,,0,0,0,,Lamento.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:06.03,Normal,,0,0,0,,Apanhei-o.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:11.55,Normal,,0,0,0,,Robe, todas a bruxas\N sabem do que fizeste.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:17.46,Normal,,0,0,0,,Majestade, por favor salva\N a Himawari e o Um Urso!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:19.53,Normal,,0,0,0,,Assim o farei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:23.95,Normal,,0,0,0,,São testemunhas das más ações dele.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:30.80,Normal,,0,0,0,,Todas estas bruxas\N foram contaminadas pelo amor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:33.97,Normal,,0,0,0,,Por isso devem\N morrer queimadas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:36.30,Normal,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:38.80,Normal,,0,0,0,,Estás a tentar queimar as evidências, é?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:42.54,Normal,,0,0,0,,Avó, faz alguma coisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:45.57,Normal,,0,0,0,,Choco!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:46.74,Normal,,0,0,0,,Avó!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:48.18,Normal,,0,0,0,,Pois é!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:52.67,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pode ser-vos útil mais tarde.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.67,0:05:56.46,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Encarem-no e gritem por socorro.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:58.68,Normal,,0,0,0,,Ajuda-nos, Himawari!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:05:59.84,Normal,,0,0,0,,Socorro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:15.60,Normal,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:17.89,Normal,,0,0,0,,Prendam-no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:18.76,Normal,,0,0,0,,Sim, senhora!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:28.49,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ficámos a salvo,\N graças ao Raiun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:31.13,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Obrigada, Himawari.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:35.79,Normal,,0,0,0,,Feliz Natal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:37.79,Normal,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:44.86,Normal,,0,0,0,,Kurotori Chiyoko,\N passaste para o nível três de bruxaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:49.01,Normal,,0,0,0,,Conseguiste, Choco!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:50.62,Normal,,0,0,0,,Ora...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:55.79,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O Natal acabou \Npor ser bastante agradável.{\i0}
